ton\" title=\"Symond Templeton\">Symond Templeton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edmund_Waxley\" title=\"Edmund Waxley\">Lord Waxley</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Anya Waynwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Waynwood\" title=\"Donnel Waynwood\">Donnel Waynwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Elys_Waynwood\" title=\"Elys Waynwood\">Elys Waynwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jasper_Waynwood\" title=\"Jasper Waynwood\">Jasper Waynwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Winged_Knight\" title=\"Winged Knight\">Winged Knight</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions\">Mentions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_41&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Mentions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:20;\">\n<p><b>Events:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Bells\" title=\"Battle of the Bells\">Battle of the Bells</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone\" title=\"Mêlée at Runestone\">Mêlée at Runestone</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"Siege of Dragonstone\">Siege of Dragonstone</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">Siege of Riverrun</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(300)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (300)\">Siege of Storm's End</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_L